dcterms:description: CryoNuSeg contains 30 images from 10 organs, each with a size of 512 × 512. The dataset is used for nuclei instance segmentation of cryosectioned H&E-stained histological images.
dcterms:title: Cryosectioned and H&E-stained Nuclei Segmentation (CryoNuSeg)

dcterms:description: DigestPath contains 69 images of the digestive system, each with a size of approximately 1500×1200. The dataset is used for pathological detection and segmentation of the digestive system.
dcterms:title: Digestive-System Pathological Segmentation (DigestPath)
